ARM: imx/mxs defconfigs: add MTD_SPI_NOR (new dependency for M25P80)

These defconfigs contain the CONFIG_M25P80 symbol, which is now
dependent on the MTD_SPI_NOR symbol. Add CONFIG_MTD_SPI_NOR to satisfy
the new dependency.

